Jorinde is the name of a series of projects. This is the general structure
of this directory and the projects.

Projects:
	- Jorinde XML
	- Jorinde HTTPD
	- Jorinde Lunit
	- Jorinde Shared Libraries
	- Jorinde Errorhandler
	- Jorinde CronD

Direct sub-projects of the httpd (located under httpd/):
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Test website
	- Jorinde HTTPD: 'Official' website (including html:ized versions of /doc)
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Documentation (/doc directory)

Several sub-components (plugins) to HTTPD (included, but replacable w/ config):
	- Jorinde HTTPD: DAV plugin
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Logger plugin
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Authorization plugin
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Error-handler plugin
	- Jorinde HTTPD: LSP mediahandler plugin
	- Jorinde HTTPD: C mediahandler plugin

Glues for libraries:
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Kernel Library Glue (default)
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Igor Glue
	- Jorinde HTTPD: Phantasmal Glue

Dependencies between projects:
	- A lot still. Things depend on each other 'upwards'.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

/usr/System/
	httpd/									Daemons used by Kernel Library
		initd.c
		lib/
		data/
		include/
		??? TODO: What to do with the rest of the daemons? Separate dir?

	/open/httpd/lib/user.c					Inheritable user object.


/usr/Jorinde/								Main directory
	jorinde.h								Include a glue.h file for your
											environment here.
	initd.c
		-> httpd/initd.c
		-> xml/initd.c
		-> lunit/initd.c
		-> plugins/initd.c (if it exists)
	doc/
		General documentation for all sub-
		projects.
	httpd/									Jorinde HTTPD
		config/								Default Configuration
		http/
		dav/
		error/
		log/
		mh/									Mediahandlers
			lsp/
			c/
	open/									Open directory
		shared/								Shared components
			include/
				shared.h
				glue/
					<various glue .h's>		For convenicence, share these.
			lib/							General purpose libraries
				string.c
				array.c
				bstr.c
				iterator.c
			data/
				bstr.c
				iterator.c
	log/									Logs for anything
		<empty dir by default>
	jxml/									Jorinde XML
	lunit/									Jorinde Lunit
	jerror/									Jorinde errorhandler
	glue/									Glue for various environments
		<phantasmal glue>
		<igor glue>
		<standard kernel-lib glue>
